Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.00,0:00:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm a soldier  而那也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.23,0:00:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.47,0:00:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同時站在火線的兩端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.14,0:00:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繞過危險的轉角  追過生與死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.61,0:00:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奔向前挑戰謊言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.49,0:00:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論編織出多少謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.16,0:00:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相還是會照出光明的輪廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.14,0:00:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.87,0:00:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.27,0:00:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當我們的痛苦都拋在腦後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.64,0:00:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.24,0:00:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.84,0:01:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是士兵不是站著就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.35,0:01:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.88,0:01:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佔好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.42,0:01:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它們留給審判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.72,0:01:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.36,0:01:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.06,0:01:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犧牲的時候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.80,0:01:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只能奮起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.60,0:01:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻殼機動隊 S.A.C 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.92,0:01:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會不會對PKF型號的義體太過自信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.16,0:01:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早就過了使用年限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.73,0:01:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼優勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.66,0:01:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意思是就算這樣你還是會贏嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.40,0:01:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽起來很不爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.94,0:01:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#21  敗逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.21,0:02:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要擊倒切斷痛覺的義體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.45,0:02:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有震動腦部了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.50,0:03:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.43,0:03:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以前是游擊隊員嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.76,0:03:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是又怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.63,0:03:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.13,0:03:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會獲勝大概是因為些微的動機差異吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.34,0:03:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還有不得不去做的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.21,0:03:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要追過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.81,0:03:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.93,0:04:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看得出來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.42,0:04:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.41,0:04:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.51,0:04:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遙控屍體？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.11,0:04:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳  想連我一起殺掉嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.52,0:04:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.85,0:04:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為射擊控制軟體的提升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.95,0:05:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以用高於你的精確度擊中針頭大小的目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.69,0:05:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.13,0:05:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙的腦前額葉什麼時候被燒燬的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.16,0:05:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經發出惡臭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.33,0:05:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且如果是遙控屍體的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.67,0:05:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這麼深的地底下要怎麼傳送電波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.64,0:05:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會不會是利用那個呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.52,0:05:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.49,0:05:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.52,0:05:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個動作是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.96,0:05:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩邊都沒人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.72,0:05:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.37,0:05:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.14,0:05:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去追久世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.67,0:05:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也追過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.04,0:05:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛的武裝機甲是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.14,0:05:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陸自沒有理由介入這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.58,0:06:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯伊爾呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.45,0:06:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齋藤先生去追了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.25,0:06:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.42,0:06:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.49,0:06:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.69,0:06:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特  你怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.46,0:06:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.50,0:06:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓那傢伙逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.77,0:06:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.94,0:06:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.21,0:06:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點大意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.77,0:06:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點去追那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.34,0:06:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波瑪他們等一下會跟上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.91,0:06:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要離開這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.18,0:06:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.72,0:06:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.15,0:06:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙很強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.43,0:06:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點出港
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.83,0:06:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追兵來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.87,0:06:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙好像下船去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.44,0:06:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們去進行交易之後  他就不見人影了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.61,0:06:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.59,0:07:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.86,0:07:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掩護我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.48,0:07:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.58,0:08:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙的目的地是長崎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.42,0:08:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救助巴特之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.55,0:08:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用傾斜旋翼機追
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.15,0:08:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.87,0:08:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.67,0:08:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.51,0:08:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特先生  你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.31,0:08:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先別管這個  少校人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.25,0:08:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偽裝船出港去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.95,0:08:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們用傾斜旋翼機追
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.26,0:08:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把巴特放到塔奇克馬後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.49,0:08:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.86,0:09:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯伊爾很久之前腦前額葉就被燒燬而死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.06,0:09:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怕俄國當局跟蹤柯伊爾之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.47,0:09:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他就已經是遙控屍體了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且我們到的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.81,0:09:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賈布羅夫與加賀崎都不在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.14,0:09:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武裝機甲的駕駛員也是遙控屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.18,0:09:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概原本是佐川的人或工地的勞工吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.65,0:09:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機甲也是陸自還沒驗收的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.95,0:09:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次交易有內幕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.92,0:09:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個應該可以成為調查久世資金支付來源的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.86,0:09:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他好像擁有令人難以置信的資金來源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.13,0:09:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.86,0:09:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這方面的追查以後再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.67,0:09:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動作快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.75,0:09:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追兵馬上就到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.28,0:09:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先繞到色丹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.32,0:09:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該有同型的偽裝船已經從出島出港了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.49,0:10:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等同伴到了之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.22,0:10:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再穿過海保的監視網\N（海上保安廳）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.26,0:10:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問題在於剛剛那些人如果從空中追過來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.19,0:10:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先準備好防空炮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.25,0:10:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.45,0:10:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老大  被打敗了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.42,0:10:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒事  不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.53,0:10:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.16,0:10:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去追久世的船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.70,0:10:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石川  把那傢伙甩下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.72,0:11:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.56,0:11:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自爆嗎  可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.09,0:12:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鉛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.39,0:12:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有追來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.33,0:12:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是他替我們擋下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.13,0:12:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.50,0:12:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交易情報洩漏給當局了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.14,0:12:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.91,0:12:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是鈽已經到手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.57,0:12:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.51,0:12:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣出島就將成為我們的國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.58,0:12:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.15,0:12:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不能太樂觀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.48,0:12:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等到送進出島再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.75,0:12:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.79,0:12:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此我有個提議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.66,0:12:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.06,0:12:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從這裏開始由我一個人前往出島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.86,0:12:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在色丹下船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.70,0:13:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再往前航行就會出現海上保安廳的巡邏艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.70,0:13:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何況不是還有走陸路這一招嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.84,0:13:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還可以欺騙警察的耳目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.91,0:13:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不  那不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.34,0:13:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從陸地無法進入出島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.51,0:13:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要進去只有從海上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.31,0:13:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何況為了宣佈獨立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.82,0:13:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿過海上保安廳的監視網\N把鈽帶進去的話比較有效果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.29,0:13:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建立在公開展示之上的核武
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.19,0:13:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢竟只是一種嚇阻力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.46,0:13:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是拿來使用的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.26,0:13:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我們就更應該去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.66,0:13:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟海保戰鬥的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.43,0:13:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一個人怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.20,0:13:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我自己一個人也能存活下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.44,0:13:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定會把鈽帶回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.97,0:13:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你們在的話只會礙手礙腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.68,0:13:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然你都說得這麼直接了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.25,0:13:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只能相信你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.86,0:13:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在300萬的難民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.62,0:14:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正在同步注視著我的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.69,0:14:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能在這裏退縮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.00,0:14:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,道警的直升機嗎\N（北海道警察）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.74,0:14:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直有種既視感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.71,0:14:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天不是也看過同樣的光景嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.68,0:14:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,課長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.88,0:14:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請優先處理巴特與石川的救助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.35,0:14:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有海上保安廳的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.35,0:14:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然很遺憾  不過還是麻煩你知會一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.56,0:14:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我帶帕茲與波瑪去調查佐川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.83,0:14:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有些事情我很在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.66,0:14:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.90,0:14:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是久世已經拿到鈽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.13,0:14:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海保就是最終防衛線了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.70,0:14:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.14,0:14:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在出島已經做好數艘同型偽裝船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.91,0:14:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請他們要特別注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.38,0:14:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從距離上考量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.84,0:14:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想他們要花幾天才會\N穿過公海出現在長崎外海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.29,0:15:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.29,0:15:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有照相館的預約嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.83,0:15:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂喂  你得了健忘癥嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.83,0:15:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是來往40年的上澤照相館\N那個繼承父業的女兒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.28,0:15:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難民嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.94,0:15:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過度無人化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.15,0:15:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許僅僅靠特殊化的才能\N已經無法生活下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.12,0:15:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們去情報處理室和記憶管理室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.82,0:15:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去社長室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.99,0:15:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.36,0:15:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是內廳導演的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.13,0:15:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很有可能沒把鈽交給久世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.33,0:15:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想找出相關證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.63,0:15:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然合田目標已經完成十之八九
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.83,0:15:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  他應該是打算製造\N難民已經先有核武的既成事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.90,0:15:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿來當作派遣自衛軍的決定性證據吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.37,0:15:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們找到東西就回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.11,0:15:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.85,0:16:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再這樣下去將會跟難民內戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.98,0:16:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現政權擴軍的想法就能實現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.22,0:16:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你打算如何解決不斷惡化的難民問題呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.99,0:16:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,合田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.74,0:16:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加賀崎嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.41,0:16:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過這邊看來是假義體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.51,0:16:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,切換到本體想要逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.52,0:16:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果還是被殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.02,0:16:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賈布羅夫與他的部下嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.73,0:16:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無人化反而害了他們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.39,0:16:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟克氯丹一樣被殺了也沒人知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.20,0:16:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部都被刪掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.00,0:16:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.97,0:16:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,克氯丹的資料就成了唯一的線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.41,0:17:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帕茲  波瑪  你們那邊如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.81,0:17:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這邊只剩下跟公司有關的記錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.08,0:17:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然有大量刪除資料的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.08,0:17:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是很難復原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.35,0:17:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這邊也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.02,0:17:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.39,0:17:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從相關狀況來判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.66,0:17:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次交易好像是在內廳的操控下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.79,0:17:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是沒有內廳操縱柯伊爾的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.30,0:17:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,記錄現場之後先回本部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.77,0:17:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解\N瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.63,0:17:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目前還是在合田掌握當中嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.34,0:17:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會怎麼做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.24,0:17:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.26,0:17:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.93,0:17:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是沒過個3天  身體還不習慣而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.40,0:18:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老傢伙的傷勢如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.94,0:18:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸好腦部沒有發現異常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.07,0:18:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概要一個月才能痊癒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.61,0:18:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次事件我們蒙受極大損失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.18,0:18:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊員的死亡  負傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.75,0:18:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連傾斜旋翼機都失去了\N可以說是徹底被打敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.46,0:18:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世的偽裝船還沒出現嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.13,0:18:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海保的監視網還沒有逮到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.26,0:18:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,政府也沒有特別的動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.03,0:18:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難民現在也很安靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.87,0:18:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家一致的見解是欠缺出動自衛軍的依據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.11,0:18:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然是透過非正式管道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.74,0:18:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  中國政府一直很關切\N我國對自治區的反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.31,0:18:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼自治區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.78,0:18:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明連難民都不肯收留
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.02,0:18:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說話態度還這麼自以為是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.19,0:18:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茅葺會被稱為親中派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.55,0:18:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許就是拿中國的發言當靠山的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.16,0:19:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在即使在海上保安廳內部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.46,0:19:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也只有一部分人知道\N偽裝船上可能載著鈽元素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.53,0:19:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但神崎議員那邊卻已經透過獨自的管道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.07,0:19:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掌握到這次的狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.01,0:19:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此應該認為在執政黨內部\N已經有不少人掌握到事情狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.11,0:19:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使如此  高倉官房長官還是按兵不動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.65,0:19:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是因為他們認為\N只要鈽照內廳的劇本被帶進出島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.59,0:19:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就會造成既成事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.12,0:19:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,排除派遣自衛軍的障礙\N所以覺得游刃有餘吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.19,0:19:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.30,0:19:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在部分網絡上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.23,0:19:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,針對俄國黑手黨和難民之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.90,0:19:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進行過鈽元素交易的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.90,0:19:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經開始出現騷動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.94,0:19:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.11,0:19:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難民那邊要怎麼出牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.14,0:19:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果正如少校的判斷\N久世並沒有拿到鈽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.55,0:19:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認為久世會怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.88,0:20:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然他用無與倫比的領袖魅力\N不尋常的行動力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.89,0:20:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及正確的情勢判斷\N將事態引導到目前這個程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.69,0:20:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  他到底還是一名恐怖份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.23,0:20:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管在戰略上或戰力上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.70,0:20:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有國家當後盾的合氏還是比他高明一籌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.57,0:20:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從結果來看久世的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.44,0:20:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像不偏離合田的劇本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.84,0:20:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,按照他的想法扮演局勢演變的推手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.38,0:20:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但實際上他並不在合田控制之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.98,0:20:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果有能夠逆轉局勢的要素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.75,0:20:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的行動或許就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.12,0:20:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然說起來有點奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.89,0:20:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是Stand Alone Complex所造成的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.76,0:20:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也說不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.83,0:20:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,課長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.73,0:20:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在有報告指出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.67,0:20:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海上保安廳的巡邏艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.67,0:20:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,於長崎外海天草灘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.54,0:20:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現可能是久世搭乘的偽裝船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.71,0:21:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在正在傳送狀況嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.08,0:21:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.81,0:21:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有來自巡邏艇的現場影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.88,0:21:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連接到這邊的螢幕上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.69,0:21:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.39,0:21:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不停船啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.73,0:21:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光嚇阻沒有用
